707290f-a.title: Brooklyn: Washington St. - York St.
707290f-a.text:
Washington Street, north from York Street, to the Manhattan Bridge,
and the East River, showing the buildings of Robert Gair Co., cardboard

About 1926.
Ewing Galloway.
